  mso-no-proof:yes'>Research Labs provide specialized facilities for your
  scientists and engineers to investigate new technologies and design new
  components.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Research is spread across three different industry type=
s:
  Weapons, Energy and HighTech</span>.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Research can only occur when a ship or base is stati=
